summary:
Experienced Owner with a demonstrated history of working in the design industry. Strong arts and design professional graduated in Design (Copenhagen, DK) and in Archeology, History of Arts, History (Sorbonne university, Paris, FR) 
Skilled in Branding & Identity. with solid marketing background and experience. Fields of activity include strategic and design thinking, concept development and visual storytelling – with applications ranging from B2B communications, branding programmes, book design, animations/motion graphics, UI&UX.
